<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="393">Fl. Trop. E. Africa, Leguminosae</emphasis>
2: 100. 1967) treated the Hermann material (distributed over two pages) as syntypes, and Larsen &amp; Larsen subsequently designated one of them as the 
<typeStatus>lectotype</typeStatus>
